Palindrome Linked-List (https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/check-if-linked-list-is-pallindrome/1)

You are given the head of a singly linked list of positive integers. 
You have to check if the given linked list is palindrome or not.

Solution:
class Solution:
    def isPalindrome(self, head):
        def check(n):
            nonlocal head
            if not n:
                return True
            r = check(n.next) and n.data == head.data
            head = head.next
            return r
        
        return check(head)
